{
  "stem": "19211.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Gordon is very interested in listening to all the details.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't want to burden them too much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Actually, he wanted to go with me to that town, when I was born, and wanted to see it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then the things started, with Yugoslavia, with the Bosnian-- the unrest, and the Russia, it changed from communist, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it just-- the unrest, and there I-- we were afraid to go there, really.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we didn't go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was more-- Gordon is more understanding, I think, than Dennis.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dennis just didn't want to hear much about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I told them basically, what went on, so they-- they should know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Here it is now, it's 50 years-- more than 50 years after the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's correct.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I think that one of the most important things on my mind is to have your own country, no matter what.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to have your own country.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think this would happen, that, badly as it did if we had Israel then.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is our only hope.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For the Jew, it's our only hope.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we are really not wanted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was proven that we were not wanted by the world.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were ships coming to Cuba.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Did you hear about that ship that came to Cuba, they rejected it and sent it back to Germany and to-- to the ovens, said they wouldn't accept the Jews.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Americans, Roosevelt had a rough time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He-- he-- maybe he wanted to accept some Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the nation, as a whole, didn't want to accept Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we are not really wanted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's the only hope, is our own country.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's the only place that you can feel safe, regardless of whether there is unrest, unrest everywhere.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
